&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">GitHub 上目前 3.4万 的Star，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">安装量超过 230 万次。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 2em;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5518518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100049052\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c5c5d79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM2ibDBMdECU2EydXwTzoSYVFomcJsKDXpUCOkTSVUO8un4711HEw3kiahYicBfPGPGHPSFd7OBiaEUKsdzHtB8niajaKsEKTctIJZeYdZdJVkWCo%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">简单说就是让你不用敲命令行，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">通过网页界面就能管理服务器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-fa